data.description: Beautiful home with plenty of space and many large rooms. This home also has a bonus building that could be used as a workshop or many other things. There is a nice foyer as you walk into the home, a wonderful home office as well as a secret entrance to the attic in an upstairs room. Located beside The Penn house mansion. Great big rooms with beautiful hardwood floors. There is a balcony. It is a must see!!
